        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">UI/UX Design</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Detailed description of the project, the problem it solved, and the impact it had. 
          This gives visitors a good sense of the work before they dive deeper.
        </p>
      </a>
    </article>

    <!-- Project 3 -->
